trend_summary: Over the sequence the landscape evolves from scattered woodland pockets to a consolidated suburb. Warehousing and retail complexes spread along the northern corridor, residential streets infill southern zones, and arterial roads are widened. A small airfield endures, while central greenbelt vegetation thickens, preserving a sizeable tree canopy amid growth.
notable_changes: Expansion of white-roof warehouses and retail blocks along the northern edge.
Construction of a large commercial complex east of the small runway on previously vacant land.
Progressive infill of cul-de-sac residential subdivisions in the southwest and southeast.
Widening of the main highway and addition of new junctions/roundabouts.
Maturing and slight expansion of central greenbelt and peripheral tree canopy.
